Jung-shim told me to apply a dozen times.

1:31:58.964 --> 1:32:01.215
Because I didn't, it's a problem.

1:32:01.216 --> 1:32:03.050
Apply for what?

1:32:03.051 --> 1:32:09.600
The verification procedure
for comfort women.

1:32:10.184 --> 1:32:13.437
I wanted to hide it and didn't do it.

1:32:14.938 --> 1:32:18.108
So there's no proof
that I was a comfort woman.

1:32:18.942 --> 1:32:21.194
Since my country can't prove it...

1:32:21.195 --> 1:32:25.991
they say I can't testify at the hearing.

1:32:26.366 --> 1:32:28.117
That's crazy!

1:32:28.118 --> 1:32:33.582
I ruined everything
because of my damn pride.

1:32:36.960 --> 1:32:38.961
Everyone!

1:32:38.962 --> 1:32:41.965
- What's he up to?
- I need your help!

1:32:42.966 --> 1:32:45.010
Please help Granny NAH Ok-boon!

1:32:45.344 --> 1:32:47.471
Please sign the petition.

1:32:48.472 --> 1:32:51.974
Please sign the petition
to help Granny NAH Ok-boon.

1:32:51.975 --> 1:32:57.856
Could you sign to help verify
the comfort women victims?

1:32:59.983 --> 1:33:02.236
Hello. Please read this.

1:33:04.655 --> 1:33:05.988
Thank you.

1:33:05.989 --> 1:33:07.289
Hello.

1:33:11.995 --> 1:33:13.295
Please read this.

1:33:17.251 --> 1:33:18.551
Director?

1:33:19.878 --> 1:33:21.879
What in the world?

1:33:21.880 --> 1:33:23.798
Why are you here during work hours?

1:33:23.799 --> 1:33:25.099
What?

1:33:25.509 --> 1:33:28.053
It's all a part of my job.

1:33:29.012 --> 1:33:31.265
I'm not signing. Stop bothering me.

1:33:32.015 --> 1:33:34.016
But it's for your own good, sir.

1:33:34.017 --> 1:33:38.938
Verifying Granny NAH as a comfort woman
is a national issue.

1:33:38.939 --> 1:33:40.898
It'll be approved eventually.

1:33:40.899 --> 1:33:44.026
The question is, who's going to do it.

1:33:44.027 --> 1:33:47.030
Congress? Mayor of Seoul?
Minister of Gender Equality?

1:33:47.656 --> 1:33:52.077
They're all looking to resolve it
and be noticed.

1:33:52.911 --> 1:33:54.211
Director,

1:33:54.538 --> 1:34:00.042
you can pass it and receive the spotlight.

1:34:00.043 --> 1:34:01.343
Not so bad, is it?

1:34:02.212 --> 1:34:06.049
Will you pass up the chance of a lifetime?

1:34:07.968 --> 1:34:10.095
MAYOR OF SEOUL

1:34:14.600 --> 1:34:16.602
MINISTER OF GENDER EQUALITY

1:34:54.014 --> 1:34:56.265
I see you're a Level 9 official.

1:34:56.266 --> 1:34:58.142
You passed the Level 7 exam?

1:34:58.143 --> 1:34:59.443
Yes.

1:35:00.354 --> 1:35:04.106
You just have one brother in high school?

1:35:04.107 --> 1:35:06.777
Yes, I only have...

1:35:11.114 --> 1:35:12.414
No.

1:35:14.618 --> 1:35:16.119
There's one more.

1:35:17.037 --> 1:35:19.790
LEVEL 7 SECOND ROUND INTERVIEWS

1:35:23.126 --> 1:35:25.628
JAPAN REJECTS NAH OK-BOON'S
COMFORT WOMAN VERIFICATION

1:35:25.629 --> 1:35:29.007
JAPAN DEMANDS HARD EVIDENCE

1:35:48.443 --> 1:35:52.447
RAYBURN HOUSE OFFICE, WASHINGTON D.C.

1:36:32.195 --> 1:36:33.495
Jung-shim...

1:36:33.947 --> 1:36:35.991
I can do this, right?

1:36:38.118 --> 1:36:39.418
Granny, here.

1:37:13.779 --> 1:37:18.909
MICHELLE VAN JANSSEN, FORCED TO COMFORT
BROTHELS BY JAPANESE IN 1942 AT AGE 21

1:37:40.430 --> 1:37:42.557
She cut off all her hair.

1:37:43.391 --> 1:37:48.396
CONGRESSMAN MICHAEL LEE, INTRODUCED
RESOLUTION HR 121 TO HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES

1:39:01.344 --> 1:39:02.762
Oh Michelle...

1:39:12.022 --> 1:39:14.024
Your testimony will begin.

1:39:53.688 --> 1:39:55.273
Will you testify?

1:43:39.122 --> 1:43:48.631
Japanese soldiers
carved these on me with knives.

1:43:53.636 --> 1:43:57.182
My body is covered with such scars.

1:43:59.058 --> 1:44:01.394
Every time I see these scars...

1:44:02.687 --> 1:44:08.318
the hellish memories come alive again.

1:44:11.029 --> 1:44:12.697
No evidence, you say?

1:44:13.323 --> 1:44:15.324
I'm the evidence!

1:44:15.325 --> 1:44:21.664
Michelle, here, and all survivors
are the evidence.

1:44:22.207 --> 1:44:24.959
When I suffered hell like that...

1:44:25.668 --> 1:44:30.840
I was only thirteen.

1:44:31.674 --> 1:44:32.974
Thirteen.

1:44:36.930 --> 1:44:39.098
I was unable to die.

1:44:41.684 --> 1:44:43.478
I missed my home

1:44:46.689 --> 1:44:51.444
and waited it out to see my family.

1:48:37.920 --> 1:48:40.673
Thank you. It was a moving speech.

1:48:42.550 --> 1:48:44.051
This way.

1:49:12.747 --> 1:49:14.047
This way.

1:49:28.846 --> 1:49:30.889
You crazy bastards!

1:49:30.890 --> 1:49:32.767
Min-jae! No, stop!

1:49:34.018 --> 1:49:35.853
Are you stupid?

1:49:36.521 --> 1:49:39.482
I don't need your filthy money!

1:49:40.608 --> 1:49:42.652
Acknowledge it and apologize.

1:49:42.860 --> 1:49:44.654
You shameless fools!

1:49:50.993 --> 1:49:53.286
Granny! Not that.

1:49:53.287 --> 1:49:54.587
Calm down.

1:49:56.791 --> 1:49:58.091
Calm down.

1:49:58.876 --> 1:50:01.170
You skipped work to come here?

1:50:02.004 --> 1:50:05.550
Without you, there's not much to do anyway.

1:50:07.927 --> 1:50:10.012
Thank you so much.

1:50:11.055 --> 1:50:13.057
I couldn't have spoken
without you.

1:50:13.757 --> 1:50:15.268
You were great.

1:50:18.938 --> 1:50:20.147
- Granny?
- Hmm?

