1:51:18.748 --> 1:51:24.128
- I missed you, sister.
- I'm so sorry for everything.

1:51:25.087 --> 1:51:26.589
I'm so sorry.

1:51:26.839 --> 1:51:29.467
Oh, Jung-nam!

1:51:34.639 --> 1:51:37.767
- I'm sorry.
- Sorry?

1:51:39.226 --> 1:51:42.145
Oh, Jung-nam!

1:51:42.146 --> 1:51:45.107
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

1:51:50.780 --> 1:51:59.663
The 'Comfort Women' Resolution (HR 121)
was passed unanimously on July 30th, 2007.

1:51:59.664 --> 1:52:05.419
