1:52:45.167 --> 1:52:47.169
Grow up.

1:52:51.173 --> 1:52:53.425
You're going to San Francisco next week?

1:52:53.426 --> 1:52:54.218
Yup.

1:52:54.219 --> 1:52:56.846
I'm speaking at the city council.

1:52:57.972 --> 1:53:01.474
Saw the news?
Abe is talking bullshit again!

1:53:01.475 --> 1:53:03.810
