1:53:03.811 --> 1:53:05.111
Damn it!

1:53:07.189 --> 1:53:09.190
Granny.

1:53:09.191 --> 1:53:11.735
Slow down. Think of your age.

1:53:11.736 --> 1:53:14.696
The Japanese are waiting
